d expanding to EU4 in W11, following successful testing in Canada. This phase encompasses three key enhancements: the integration of localized, market-relevant verbiage within headline copy to better resonate with regional audiences; updates to the mobile experience and layout; and the implementation of current, on-brand visuals to ensure consistent brand presentation. The successful Canadian pilot validated the MCS optimizations made with an expected CVR lift of 50% in EU5 on tested LPs. Projected impact is included in OP2 registration, not additional. Results will be available EOM April due to OCI tech readiness data exclusions across EU3."}, "1211898253103683": {"name": "Help Needed flag", "value": "No"}, "1211898253103663": {"name": "Impact (EU Reg)", "value": "14000"}, "1211898253103687": {"name": "Status L-week", "value": "Green - On track"}, "1212629048694011": {"name": "Marketplace/Region", "value": "EU5"}}' AS JSON), CURRENT_TIMESTAMP)
